title: [Veythorne Manor, Gardens]
description: Swirling shadows line the path to the northwest, only the palest highlights of dark green illuminated by the sun's rays.  White sprigs of jasmine trail along the ground, and faint echoes of the whistling wind filter in from afar.  Dark creeper vines twirl among the jasmine, each slowly ascending toward the heavens upon the bark of the surrounding trees.
